      <title>巴西央行立场转为鹰派 准备加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/brazil-central-bank-won-t-hesitate-to-hike-rates-if-appropriate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行表示，随着通胀前景恶化，它将毫不犹豫地提高利率，这标志着在暂停货币宽松周期仅一个月后，央行指导方针发生了重大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/brazil-central-bank-won-t-hesitate-to-hike-rates-if-appropriate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡特彼勒表示 2024 年利润将高于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/caterpillar-profit-beats-estimates-boosted-by-stronger-pricing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡特彼勒公司 (Caterpillar Inc.) 表示，其年度利润可能高于此前预期，因为尽管对全球经济的担忧日益加剧，但该公司报告的第二季度收益仍显示出韧性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/caterpillar-profit-beats-estimates-boosted-by-stronger-pricing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:33:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称在标普 5% 下跌后买入通常可获利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/goldman-says-buying-s-p-500-after-5-drop-is-usually-profitable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团对四十年数据的分析显示，在过去一个月出现如此大规模的暴跌之后买入美国股票通常都是有利可图的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/goldman-says-buying-s-p-500-after-5-drop-is-usually-profitable</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 09:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
